  <!-- How this differs note -->
  <div class="container-wide pt-4">
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--bg-2)] px-6 py-4 text-sm text-ink-300">
      <strong class="text-ink-100">How this guide differs from our other tool resources:</strong> This is the <em>evergreen workflow guide</em> — tools organised strictly by the job they perform at each stage of your GEO programme, regardless of the year. It does not cover what is new or changed recently. For that, see the <a href="/best-geo-tools-2026/" class="text-accent-400 underline decoration-accent-500/30 underline-offset-2 hover:text-accent-300">Best GEO Tools 2026 annual roundup</a>. For a full category overview independent of workflow order, see the <a href="/geo-tools/" class="text-accent-400 underline decoration-accent-500/30 underline-offset-2 hover:text-accent-300">GEO Tools hub</a>. For head-to-head platform evaluation criteria, see the <a href="/geo-tools-comparison/" class="text-accent-400 underline decoration-accent-500/30 underline-offset-2 hover:text-accent-300">GEO tools comparison</a>. For zero-cost starting points, see <a href="/free-geo-tools/" class="text-accent-400 underline decoration-accent-500/30 underline-offset-2 hover:text-accent-300">free GEO tools</a>.
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Sticky TOC -->
  <nav aria-label="On this page" class="container-wide pb-4 lg:pb-0">
    <div class="card px-6 py-4 lg:sticky lg:top-[calc(var(--header-h)+1rem)] lg:z-10">
      <span class="font-mono text-xs text-ink-500 uppercase tracking-widest">On this page</span>
      <ol class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-sm text-ink-300">
        <li><a href="#why-job-based" class="hover:text-[var(--accent)] transition-colors">Why job-based matters</a></li>
        <li><a href="#audit-tools" class="hover:text-[var(--accent)] transition-colors">Audit tools</a></li>
        <li><a href="#optimisation-tools" class="hover:text-[var(--accent)] transition-colors">Optimisation tools</a></li>
        <li><a href="#monitoring-tools" class="hover:text-[var(--accent)] transition-colors">Monitoring tools</a></li>
        <li><a href="#reporting-tools" class="hover:text-[var(--accent)] transition-colors">Reporting tools</a></li>
        <li><a href="#workflow-table" class="hover:text-[var(--accent)] transition-colors">Workflow table</a></li>
        <li><a href="#stack-guidance" class="hover:text-[var(--accent)] transition-colors">Stack guidance</a></li>
